    <h1>TikTok Stitch</h1>
    <p class="description">A TikTok feature that lets you clip up to 5 seconds from any public video and use it as the intro to your response. The <strong>go-to format for commentary, fact-checks, and opinion content</strong> on TikTok.</p>
